reviewText: Love this Kundalini Awakened CD Thank
Having taken some reiki classes in the past I wanted to broaden my base of metaphysical knowledge. This video had all I wanted to know and more. I have recommended it to my friends.

This DVD is not what I expected.  I expected an explanation about Kundalini Reiki which the description suggested I would get.  Instead, I got to watch a whole bunch of interviews not even related to the title of the DVD.

I couldn't be more disappointed in a dvd as this one.

This dvd does NOT have any kundalini practice what so ever. The whole reason for purchasing this dvd was to further my practice at home not listen to an interview. This dvd also looks new and even says from 2012 but the interview looks like it comes from the 70's....totally old!
